<subSubSection pageId="18" pageNumber="123" type="conservation status">
<paragraph pageId="18" pageNumber="123">Conservation status.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="18" pageNumber="123">
The red list of the IUCN ver. 3.1 assigned the category &quot;Least Concern&quot; to 
<taxonomicName class="Mammalia" family="Cricetidae" genus="Wiedomys" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Wiedomys pyrrhorhinos" order="Rodentia" pageId="18" pageNumber="123" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="pyrrhorhinos">Wiedomys pyrrhorhinos</taxonomicName>
(see 
<bibRefCitation author="Marinho-Filho, J" pageId="36" pageNumber="141" url="https://doi.org/10.2305/IUCN.UK.2008.RLTS.T23076A9415389.en" year="2016">Marinho-Filho and Langguth 2016</bibRefCitation>
). The species was not included in the official list of threatened species of Brazil (
<bibRefCitation author="Iack-Ximenes, GE" pageId="36" pageNumber="141" url="http://www.icmbio.gov.br/portal/images/stories/comunicacao/publicacoes/publicacoes-diversas/dcom_sumario_executivo_livro_vermelho_ed_2016.pdf" year="2016">ICMBIO-MMA 2016</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
